## 6. Ratio Definitions & Formulas

### Profitability

ROA  
`RATIO_ROA = INC_net_income_2025 / BAL_avg_assets`

Result: 5.86%

Interpretation: Efficient asset utilization.

ROE  
`RATIO_ROE = INC_net_income_2025 / BAL_avg_equity`

Result: 7.84%

Interpretation: Moderate shareholder return generation.

Current Ratio  
`RATIO_Current=BAL_current_assets_2025/BAL_current_liabilities_2025`

Result: 4.03x

Interpretation: Strong liquidity position.

Interest Coverage  
`RATIO_InterestCoverage=INC_ebit_2025/INC_interest_expense_2025`

